OL,4,CCovid response, public inquiry finds
OL,6,FPolitical division and disputes led to
OL,7,F"chaotic and marred decision making"
OL,8,Fby the Northern Ireland Executive
OL,9,Fduring the Covid-19 pandemic, a public
OL,10,Finquiry has concluded.
OL,12,FBaroness Heather Hallett's report on
OL,13,Fthe governmental responses to Covid -
OL,14,Fpublished on Thursday - found that the
OL,15,Fpolitical response to the public
OL,16,Fhealth emergency was "deeply divided
OL,17,Falong political lines" leading to an
OL,18,F"incoherent approach."
