OL,6,FThe report concluded that the response
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland, like the rest of
OL,8,Fthe UK, was "a repeated case of too
OL,9,Flittle, too late".
OL,11,FIt said "the devolved administrations
OL,12,Fwere too reliant on the UK government
OL,13,Fto lead the response".
OL,15,FIt further stated that in Northern
OL,16,FIreland, as in Scotland, Covid-19 was
OL,17,Fonly discussed under "any other
OL,18,Fbusiness" in meetings in late February
OL,19,F2020.
