OL,6,FIt added: "In the weeks that followed,
OL,7,FExecutive Committee meetings were
OL,8,Fdeeply divided along political lines
OL,9,Fand beset by leaks, leading to an
OL,10,Fincoherent approach in which the
OL,11,Fcircuit breaker restrictions were
OL,12,Fextended for one week, then lapsed for
OL,13,Fone week, before being reintroduced
OL,14,Ffor two further weeks ` with the one-
OL,15,Fweek lapse in restrictions correlating
OL,16,Fwith a 25% increase in cases."
